        "en": "The trend charts need time series. Enable history logging (adapter 'history', 'sql' or 'influxdb') on this instance's live.* datapoints (grid modes: live.gridNetOrigW, live.gridNetSimW, live.batteryPowerW; PV mode: live.pvW, live.consumptionW, live.directUseW) and on battery.soc.percent. For the monthly view additionally on economics.savingsTotal.eur. Without logging the evaluation only shows current values.",
